pullrequest.title: ur10 robot taken from ros-industrial for testing in gazebo

content.raw:
John, the archive I sent you was processed through the converter and any empty tags output by the converter were cleaned out.  It is the 'lean and mean' version of the file.  Also, the structure reflects that it is specifically just the ur10 and not the broader ur collection.

I have the converted file in my own repo, so if I need the sdf for future use, I have it at hand.  Whether or not you incorporate it into greater gazebo won't affect me at this time.
